HB 660 Original 2026 Regular Session Egan
Abstract: Increases the salary of assistant district attorneys on July 1, 2026.
Present law provides that, effective July 1, 2021, assistant district attorneys statewide are to
receive an annual salary of $50,000 payable monthly.
Proposed law increases the salary of the assistant district attorneys to $50,500 beginning July
1, 2026.
Effective July 1, 2026.
(Amends R.S. 16:11(A)(1))
